                        <p class="text-size-sm">Welcome! This page will help you set up and utilize our powerful satellite tracking and prediction capabilities. SatTrack-Arcturus is a robust RESTful API crafted with Node.js and Express, specifically engineered to predict satellite orbits using the Simplified General Perturbations-4 (SGP4) model.</p>
                        <h2 class="text-size-md mt-5 mb-2">Create an Account</h2>
                        <p class="text-size-sm">To start using our APIs, sign up for an account using our registration page. After filling in your details and agreeing to our terms, proceed to your account dashboard and follow the next step.</p>
                        <h2 class="text-size-md mt-5 mb-2">Generate a Key</h2>
                        <p class="text-size-sm">From your account dashboard, locate and click <strong class="text-color-blue">Keys</strong>. This will take you to a page where you can create and manage your API keys.</p>
